	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "69404d27-13b7-4a07-a509-e202b339a82c",
		"name": "users",
		"description": "# Users API Documentation\n\n## Base URL\n\nAll endpoints are prefixed with: `{{base_url}}`\n\n> ⚠️ **Important:** All endpoints in this section require **authentication**.  \nA valid **session/token** must be provided in the request headers. \n  \n\n---\n\n# Admin Endpoints\n\nThese endpoints can only be accessed by **admin accounts**.\n\n---\n\n# Upload Image to User\n\nUpload an image to a specific user account.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/users/admin/upload-to-user/:userId`\n\n### Request\n\n**Content-Type:** `multipart/form-data`\n\n| Key | Type | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| image | file | Image file to upload |\n\nExample (Form Data)\n\n```\nkey: image\nvalue: image file\n\n ```\n\n### Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Image uploaded successfully to user\",\n  \"image\": {\n    \"id\": \"cmmnd0z3m0000pp3wr84oxags\",\n    \"url\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dstj5eqcd/image/upload/v1773313423/taskmaster/user-images/cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox-1773313419952.png\",\n    \"filename\": \"taskmaster/user-images/cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox-1773313419952\",\n    \"uploadedAt\": \"2026-03-12T11:03:44.049Z\"\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# Fetch User Dashboard (Recent Changes)\n\nRetrieve a user's **latest activity**, including their most recent submission and uploaded image.\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /api/users/admin/user-dashboard/:userId`\n\n### Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": \"cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox\",\n    \"name\": \"Tunji Akande\",\n    \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n    \"memberSince\": \"2026-03-12T10:43:19.851Z\"\n  },\n  \"mostRecentSubmission\": {\n    \"id\": \"cmmne0i500000ce3wltgidhp4\",\n    \"companyName\": \"Tech Solutions Ltd\",\n    \"numberOfUsers\": 50,\n    \"numberOfProducts\": 150,\n    \"percentage\": 300,\n    \"submittedAt\": \"2026-03-12T11:31:21.683Z\"\n  },\n  \"recentImage\": {\n    \"id\": \"cmmnd0z3m0000pp3wr84oxags\",\n    \"url\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dstj5eqcd/image/upload/v1773313423/taskmaster/user-images/cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox-1773313419952.png\",\n    \"filename\": \"taskmaster/user-images/cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox-1773313419952\",\n    \"uploadedBy\": \"Admin\",\n    \"uploadedAt\": \"2026-03-12T11:03:44.049Z\"\n  },\n  \"hasData\": true,\n  \"hasImage\": true\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# Fetch All Users\n\nRetrieve a paginated list of **users and admins** with optional filtering and search.\n\n**Endpoint:**\n\n```\nGET /api/users/admin/users?search=tunji&role=USER&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc&page=1&limit=10\n\n ```\n\n### Query Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n| --- | --- |\n| search | Search users by name or email |\n| role | Filter by role (`USER` or `ADMIN`) |\n| sortBy | Field to sort results |\n| sortOrder | `asc` or `desc` |\n| page | Page number |\n| limit | Number of results per page |\n\n### Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox\",\n      \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n      \"firebaseUid\": \"YO2TrOAIIuWwyvCmtYjSuwgQeUn1\",\n      \"fullName\": \"Tunji Akande\",\n      \"role\": \"USER\",\n      \"isEmailVerified\": true,\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:43:19.851Z\",\n      \"updatedAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:43:55.290Z\",\n      \"companyData\": {\n        \"id\": \"cmmnhtizw0002dp3wny2uw3z4\",\n        \"companyName\": \"Starlab\",\n        \"numberOfUsers\": 60,\n        \"numberOfProducts\": 200,\n        \"percentage\": 333.33\n      },\n      \"receivedImages\": []\n    }\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"page\": 1,\n    \"limit\": 10,\n    \"total\": 2,\n    \"totalUsers\": 1,\n    \"totalAdmins\": 1,\n    \"pages\": 1\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# Fetch User by ID\n\nRetrieve complete details for a specific user.\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /api/users/admin/users/:userId`\n\n### Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"id\": \"cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox\",\n  \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n  \"firebaseUid\": \"YO2TrOAIIuWwyvCmtYjSuwgQeUn1\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Tunji Akande\",\n  \"role\": \"USER\",\n  \"isEmailVerified\": true,\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:43:19.851Z\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:43:55.290Z\",\n  \"companyData\": {\n    \"companyName\": \"Starlab\",\n    \"numberOfUsers\": 60,\n    \"numberOfProducts\": 200,\n    \"percentage\": 333.33\n  },\n  \"receivedImages\": []\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# Fetch Users Statistics\n\nRetrieve statistics about users and admins.\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /api/users/admin/users/stats`\n\n### Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"total\": {\n    \"users\": 1,\n    \"admins\": 1,\n    \"all\": 2\n  },\n  \"active\": {\n    \"usersWithCompanyData\": 3\n  },\n  \"recent\": {\n    \"users\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox\",\n        \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n        \"fullName\": \"Tunji Akande\",\n        \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:43:19.851Z\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"admins\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"cmmn9jnm00005n23wdb8f4cbr\",\n        \"email\": \"shopmate400@gmail.com\",\n        \"fullName\": \"Admin\",\n        \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-12T09:26:17.160Z\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# User Endpoints\n\nThese endpoints are accessible to **authenticated users**.\n\n---\n\n# Submit Company Data\n\nSubmit company information associated with the logged-in user.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/users/company-data`\n\n### Request Body\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"companyName\": \"Tech Solutions Ltd\",\n  \"numberOfUsers\": 50,\n  \"numberOfProducts\": 150\n}\n\n ```\n\n### Percentage Calculation\n\nThe **percentage value** is automatically calculated using:\n\n```\n(numberOfProducts / numberOfUsers) * 100\n\n ```\n\n### Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Company data created successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"cmmncbxsc0004xj3wq0j9qzbu\",\n    \"companyName\": \"Tech Solutions Ltd\",\n    \"numberOfUsers\": 50,\n    \"numberOfProducts\": 150,\n    \"percentage\": 300,\n    \"userId\": \"cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:44:15.948Z\",\n    \"updatedAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:44:15.948Z\"\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n---\n\n## User Profile\n\nRetrieve the **authenticated user's profile information**, including:\n\n- account details\n    \n- submitted company data\n    \n- images uploaded by admins\n    \n- total image count\n    \n\n> 🔒 **Authentication Required** \n  \n\n**Endpoint**\n\n```\nGET /api/users/profile\n\n ```\n\n### Success Response (200)\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"id\": \"cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox\",\n  \"email\": \"akandetunji2@gmail.com\",\n  \"firebaseUid\": \"YO2TrOAIIuWwyvCmtYjSuwgQeUn1\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Tunji Akande\",\n  \"role\": \"USER\",\n  \"isEmailVerified\": true,\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:43:19.851Z\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2026-03-12T10:43:55.290Z\",\n  \"companyData\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"cmmo527pa000ayl3wt793t9du\",\n      \"companyName\": \"Starlab\",\n      \"numberOfUsers\": 23,\n      \"numberOfProducts\": 45,\n      \"percentage\": 195.65,\n      \"userId\": \"cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-13T00:08:31.102Z\",\n      \"updatedAt\": \"2026-03-13T00:08:31.102Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"receivedImages\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"cmmo358iz0004yl3w3pfyne86\",\n      \"filename\": \"taskmaster/user-images/cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox-1773357289581\",\n      \"originalName\": \"VPC-eu-north-1-03-06-2026_04_03_PM.png\",\n      \"path\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dstj5eqcd/image/upload/v1773357292/taskmaster/user-images/cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox-1773357289581.png\",\n      \"mimetype\": \"image/png\",\n      \"size\": 181982,\n      \"uploadedById\": \"cmmn9jnm00005n23wdb8f4cbr\",\n      \"userId\": \"cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-12T23:14:52.906Z\",\n      \"uploadedBy\": {\n        \"id\": \"cmmn9jnm00005n23wdb8f4cbr\",\n        \"fullName\": \"Admin\",\n        \"email\": \"shopmate400@gmail.com\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"cmmo32cms0003yl3w0gm282g8\",\n      \"filename\": \"taskmaster/user-images/cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox-1773357153064\",\n      \"originalName\": \"Route-53-dashboard-Route-53-Global-03-06-2026_04_00_PM.png\",\n      \"path\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dstj5eqcd/image/upload/v1773357157/taskmaster/user-images/cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox-1773357153064.png\",\n      \"mimetype\": \"image/png\",\n      \"size\": 263012,\n      \"uploadedById\": \"cmmn9jnm00005n23wdb8f4cbr\",\n      \"userId\": \"cmmncaqi30001xj3w7i6kkwox\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-12T23:12:38.260Z\",\n      \"uploadedBy\": {\n        \"id\": \"cmmn9jnm00005n23wdb8f4cbr\",\n        \"fullName\": \"Admin\",\n        \"email\": \"shopmate400@gmail.com\"\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"imageCount\": 4\n}\n\n ```\n\n### Response Fields\n\n| Field | Description |\n| --- | --- |\n| id | Unique user identifier |\n| email | User email address |\n| fullName | User full name |\n| role | Account role (`USER` or `ADMIN`) |\n| companyData | List of company submissions by the user |\n| receivedImages | Images uploaded by admins for the user |\n| imageCount | Total number of images uploaded to the user |\n\n---",
